HW10: Data Visualization I

Alissa Seal

24 July 2020

Install and load libraries

library(tidyverse)
library(here)
library(GGally)
library(patchwork)

Import Sparrows Data

sparrows_raw <- read_tsv(here("data", "sparrows.txt"))
Parsed with column specification:
cols(
  wingcrd = col_double(),
  flatwing = col_double(),
  tarsus = col_double(),
  head = col_double(),
  culmen = col_double(),
  nalospi = col_double(),
  wt = col_double(),
  bandstat = col_double(),
  initials = col_double(),
  Year = col_double(),
  Month = col_double(),
  Day = col_double(),
  Location = col_double(),
  SpeciesCode = col_double(),
  Sex = col_double(),
  Age = col_double()
)

Check

sparrows_raw

Wrangle Sparrow Data

sparrows <- sparrows_raw %>% 
  mutate(box_group = "Sparrows",
         row_order = 1:nrow(.))

Check

view(sparrows)

Figure 2: Outliers

Run Code

plot_box<- sparrows %>% 
  ggplot(aes(x = box_group, y = wingcrd)) +
  geom_boxplot(width = 0.25) +
  labs(x = NULL, y = "Wing length (mm)")

Run Cleveland dot plot

plot_cleveland <- sparrows %>%
  ggplot(aes(x= wingcrd,y=row_order))+
  geom_point()+
  labs(x="Wing length (mm)", y="Order of the date")

Display plots

plot_box+plot_cleveland

Add coord_flip()

plot_box+plot_cleveland+coord_flip()

Figure 5: Distibution

h1 <- sparrows %>%
  filter(Month %in% 6:8) %>% 
  ggplot() +
  geom_histogram(aes(x = wt),
                 binwidth = 0.5,
                 boundary = 0,
                 closed = "right",
                 color = "black") +
  scale_x_continuous(breaks = seq(14, 28, by = 2))

Faceted histogram

h2 <- sparrows %>%
  filter(Month %in% 6:8) %>% 
  mutate(Month = case_when(
    Month == 6 ~ "June",
    Month == 7 ~ "July",
    Month == 8 ~ "August")) %>% 
  ggplot() +
  geom_histogram(aes(x = wt),
                 binwidth = 0.5,
                 boundary = 0,
                 color = "black") +
  scale_x_continuous(breaks = seq(14, 28, by = 2)) +
  facet_wrap(~ Month, ncol = 1)

Patchwork

h1+h2

Recreate figure using density

Create plot 1

dens1 <- sparrows %>%
  filter(Month %in% 6:8) %>% 
  ggplot() +
  geom_density(aes(x = wt))+
  scale_x_continuous(breaks = seq(14,  28, by = 2))

Create plot 2

dens2 <- sparrows %>%
  filter(Month %in% 6:8) %>% 
  mutate(Month = case_when(
    Month == 6 ~ "June",
    Month == 7 ~ "July",
    Month == 8 ~ "August")) %>% 
  ggplot() +
  geom_density(aes(x = wt, fill=Month), alpha=0.50) +
  scale_x_continuous(breaks = seq(14, 28, by = 2))

Patching density plots together

dens1+dens2

Figure 11: Interactions

month_order = c("May", "June", "July", "August", "September")
Warning messages:
1: In readChar(file, size, TRUE) : truncating string with embedded nuls
2: In readChar(file, size, TRUE) : truncating string with embedded nuls

sparrows %>% 
  filter(Month %in% 5:9,
         Sex != 0) %>% 
  mutate(Month = case_when(
    Month == 5 ~ "May",
    Month == 6 ~ "June",
    Month == 7 ~ "July",
    Month == 8 ~ "August",
    Month == 9 ~ "September"),
    Month = factor(Month, levels = month_order, ordered = TRUE),
    Sex = ifelse(Sex == 4, "Male", "Female")) %>% 
  ggplot(aes(x = wingcrd,
             y = wt)) +
  geom_point() +
  geom_smooth(method = "lm", se = FALSE) +
  facet_grid(Sex ~ Month)
